WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:41.000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.930
[Episode 37]

01:50.000 --> 01:50.860
How's it going?

01:53.400 --> 01:54.280
Don't worry.

01:54.930 --> 01:57.330
I've found someone
to take the fall for you.

01:58.910 --> 01:59.830
Good.

02:00.960 --> 02:02.120
That's good.

02:03.450 --> 02:04.560
Your people, though—

02:04.560 --> 02:05.600
how did they work?

02:05.620 --> 02:06.950
It got found out so fast.

02:07.080 --> 02:08.340
And you're one to talk.

02:08.669 --> 02:10.870
The difference you made in the quote
and the construction period was too small.

02:10.870 --> 02:12.530
Who wouldn't get suspicious?

02:15.080 --> 02:16.480
A miss is as good as a mile.

02:16.560 --> 02:17.420
I got careless.

02:19.020 --> 02:19.860
So what now?

02:21.440 --> 02:23.090
We'll figure it out as we go.

02:23.120 --> 02:24.800
Let's just close this case first.

02:24.800 --> 02:25.410
By the way,

02:25.690 --> 02:27.590
don't come to my place for a while.

02:27.890 --> 02:29.240
We don't want to raise suspicion.

02:29.240 --> 02:29.750
I know.

02:30.820 --> 02:32.350
Then my bid...

02:32.630 --> 02:33.560
Alright,

02:33.560 --> 02:34.490
I know what to do.

02:34.870 --> 02:36.000
We'll play it by ear.

02:39.630 --> 02:40.280
Okay.

02:43.960 --> 02:44.480
Marcos,

02:45.000 --> 02:45.470
I really

02:46.350 --> 02:47.600
let you down.

02:48.470 --> 02:49.880
On behalf of the hotel,

02:50.030 --> 02:53.079
I sincerely apologize
to you and your group.

02:55.680 --> 02:57.880
An apology won't solve the problem now.

02:58.430 --> 02:59.890
Do you understand, Kenny?

03:01.220 --> 03:03.840
Before we have the investigation results,

03:04.320 --> 03:05.620
we will cover all your expenses

03:05.620 --> 03:07.020
during your stay.

03:07.460 --> 03:10.120
I hope you can hold off
on holding us accountable

03:10.400 --> 03:12.460
and give us some time to investigate.

03:13.310 --> 03:15.440
I personally trust Miyu's character,

03:15.840 --> 03:17.470
and I don't want to
put you in a difficult position.

03:17.470 --> 03:18.920
But this time, Kenny,

03:19.190 --> 03:22.250
I represent the interests
of the entire Liberty Group.

03:22.460 --> 03:23.610
I can't let emotions get in the way.

03:23.610 --> 03:24.300
I'm sorry,

03:24.910 --> 03:27.570
but I need to call the police
as soon as possible.

03:28.150 --> 03:28.800
Marcos,

03:30.280 --> 03:31.190
I promise you.

03:31.600 --> 03:32.860
I just need three days.

03:33.310 --> 03:35.400
In three days, I will definitely give you

03:35.400 --> 03:36.730
and Liberty an answer.

03:37.400 --> 03:38.030
Kenny,

03:38.950 --> 03:40.480
This time, you may very well

03:40.710 --> 03:42.970
have to choose between the hotel and her.

03:44.930 --> 03:45.770
I know.

03:46.870 --> 03:47.470
Alright.

03:48.020 --> 03:49.079
Three days, right?

03:50.210 --> 03:51.140
Just three days.

04:08.980 --> 04:10.440
When will you give it to me?

04:11.180 --> 04:13.380
You messed up and you still want a bonus?

04:13.850 --> 04:15.000
Every single thing you asked me to do,

04:15.000 --> 04:16.480
I did right.

04:17.100 --> 04:19.310
It's just the Liberty Group
was well prepared.

04:19.310 --> 04:20.839
If you want to blame anyone,

04:21.089 --> 04:24.020
blame yourselves
for walking right into their trap.

04:25.830 --> 04:27.910
Still talking tough. Let me tell you,

04:28.390 --> 04:31.360
they're very unhappy
with how this turned out.

04:31.830 --> 04:33.390
Now that things are messed up,

04:33.390 --> 04:35.070
everything is up in the air.

04:35.510 --> 04:36.390
You'd better think about

04:36.390 --> 04:38.270
how to clean up this mess.

04:49.290 --> 04:57.900
[Purong Hotel]

04:49.720 --> 04:51.190
Ms. Xu is very insistent.

04:51.800 --> 04:53.630
She said she never
bought a bug,

04:54.070 --> 04:55.680
nor did she plant one

04:55.680 --> 04:56.830
in Mr. Marcos' room.

04:57.070 --> 04:58.110
Enough already.

04:58.480 --> 04:59.480
So the bug grew legs

04:59.480 --> 05:01.140
and walked in there on its own?

05:01.480 --> 05:03.510
But we also checked Ms. Xu's phone.

05:03.870 --> 05:05.800
Her phone has a lock screen passcode.

05:05.800 --> 05:06.430
No one but her

05:06.430 --> 05:07.920
can unlock the phone

05:07.920 --> 05:09.320
and pair it with a device.

05:09.560 --> 05:11.430
And Ms. Xu herself admitted

05:12.000 --> 05:14.440
that she personally delivered the vase

05:15.040 --> 05:16.230
where the bug

05:16.230 --> 05:18.030
was found into Mr. Marcos' room.

05:18.870 --> 05:20.480
Why would a salesperson

05:20.720 --> 05:23.630
go to a guest's room to deliver a vase?

05:24.000 --> 05:24.870
Explain that.

05:26.040 --> 05:27.240
It was a gift Ms. Xu

05:27.400 --> 05:29.520
specially prepared for Mr. Marcos.

05:29.540 --> 05:30.890
Marcos knew about it.

05:34.040 --> 05:36.250
Did you check Ms. Xu's chat logs

05:36.480 --> 05:37.230
with others?

05:37.260 --> 05:37.920
Yes, I did.

05:38.350 --> 05:41.040
All her communications
with guests were normal.

05:41.040 --> 05:42.560
As for Niu Qiankun,

05:42.020 --> 05:43.860
[Purong Hotel]

05:42.560 --> 05:43.390
whom Mr. Marcos suspects

05:43.390 --> 05:44.630
may be behind this,

05:44.920 --> 05:47.720
Ms. Xu doesn't even
have his contact information.

05:49.870 --> 05:50.430
Mr. Ji,

05:51.720 --> 05:52.510
By raising these questions

05:52.510 --> 05:55.120
about motive to obscure
the facts of the crime,

05:55.830 --> 05:58.090
are you trying to cover up for a criminal?

05:59.600 --> 06:01.530
I'm just stating objective facts.

06:02.310 --> 06:03.240
But you, Mr. Wei,

06:03.680 --> 06:05.600
keep calling a hotel employee a criminal

06:05.600 --> 06:07.930
before the chain of evidence's complete.

06:08.160 --> 06:09.510
Could I also assume

06:09.510 --> 06:11.300
that you're framing her on purpose?

06:11.300 --> 06:12.630
That's enough, Ji Feng.

06:13.890 --> 06:15.600
Stop being so hypocritical.

06:17.160 --> 06:17.800
Do you think I don't know

06:17.800 --> 06:20.000
you're deliberately covering for her?

06:20.550 --> 06:21.920
Everyone

06:21.940 --> 06:24.240
at Purong Hotel knows about

06:24.240 --> 06:25.370
your relationship.

06:26.540 --> 06:27.390
Let me tell you,

06:27.390 --> 06:29.130
you'd better stay out of this.

06:29.200 --> 06:30.630
Otherwise, you'll turn everyone
against you,

06:30.630 --> 06:33.230
and you won't even
have your own job to protect.

06:34.530 --> 06:35.040
You.

06:35.310 --> 06:36.870
Xu Miyu was caught red-handed.

06:36.870 --> 06:37.720
Fire her immediately.

06:37.720 --> 06:38.430
Put her on the blacklist

06:38.430 --> 06:40.340
of the National Hotel Association.

06:40.340 --> 06:41.159
Let everyone see

06:41.159 --> 06:43.190
Purong's attitude towards her behavior.

06:43.190 --> 06:45.050
Don't you dare lay a finger on her!

06:45.320 --> 06:46.090
Mr. Ji!

06:59.340 --> 07:00.430
I thought

07:00.460 --> 07:01.920
that with your professionalism,

07:01.920 --> 07:04.720
you'd be more calm and composed
at a time like this.

07:06.870 --> 07:08.800
Aunt, you saw all of that, didn't you?

07:08.800 --> 07:09.830
But don't worry.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.120
I'm already working on it.

07:11.120 --> 07:13.250
I won't let Purong Hotel be disgraced.

07:13.670 --> 07:14.700
Chairwoman,

07:14.720 --> 07:16.980
Xu Miyu wouldn't do something like this.

07:18.160 --> 07:19.220
I will take the lead

07:19.560 --> 07:21.600
in forming a board investigative committee

07:21.600 --> 07:23.860
to personally investigate this matter.

07:24.300 --> 07:26.910
I will not wrong an innocent person,

07:27.290 --> 07:30.050
but I won't let
any guilty person go either.

07:30.940 --> 07:31.560
Chairwoman—

07:31.560 --> 07:34.270
Stay out of this matter.

07:34.720 --> 07:35.680
Don't forget,

07:36.290 --> 07:38.950
you're still
the general manager of this hotel.

08:10.220 --> 08:11.390
The vase you just mentioned

08:11.390 --> 08:13.690
was indeed delivered
by me to Marcos' room.

08:13.690 --> 08:15.690
And I was the only one who handled it.

08:16.310 --> 08:18.240
And Ms. Xu herself admitted

08:18.240 --> 08:20.690
that she personally delivered the vase

08:21.240 --> 08:22.480
where the bug

08:22.480 --> 08:24.280
was found into Mr. Marcos' room.

08:27.800 --> 08:28.840
Where are you going?

08:28.840 --> 08:30.170
The surveillance room.

08:36.970 --> 08:37.440
Hello?

08:39.480 --> 08:40.510
Okay. Got it.

08:42.309 --> 08:44.480
They said the investigation team
will be here soon.

08:44.480 --> 08:44.960
Then we probably

08:44.960 --> 08:46.560
won't have time to eat later.

08:46.750 --> 08:48.550
Should we grab a meal first?

08:48.800 --> 08:50.160
You're right. Let's go.

09:17.290 --> 09:20.500
[Surveillance Footage]

09:20.500 --> 09:21.040
[Executive Corridor]

09:23.280 --> 09:25.410
[Camera 01]

09:28.110 --> 09:31.850
[Camera 01]

09:33.150 --> 09:38.100
[Camera 01]

09:39.960 --> 09:44.980
[Camera 01]

09:47.180 --> 09:50.310
[Camera 01]

09:54.810 --> 10:03.840
[Camera 01]

10:28.730 --> 10:30.840
The investigation team is coming
to check the surveillance footage.

10:30.840 --> 10:32.440
I had a feeling you'd be here.

10:33.930 --> 10:34.770
Looks like

10:35.100 --> 10:36.320
Xu Miyu

10:36.320 --> 10:38.180
is really being framed this time.

10:39.160 --> 10:40.220
I heard

10:40.240 --> 10:42.040
it was just some crappy phone app

10:42.060 --> 10:43.260
and a few statements.

10:43.550 --> 10:45.270
If you had stalled them for a few days,

10:45.270 --> 10:47.550
maybe she'd still have a chance.

10:47.840 --> 10:50.170
But now with this surveillance footage

10:49.220 --> 10:51.770
[Camera 01]

10:50.200 --> 10:52.200
proving that no one entered that room

10:52.200 --> 10:53.930
after the vase was placed in it,

10:54.270 --> 10:55.200
what do we do now?

10:55.480 --> 10:58.010
The investigation team
is already upstairs.

10:58.510 --> 10:59.870
With this footage,

10:59.870 --> 11:01.470
it's enough to get her fired.

11:01.940 --> 11:03.180
But it's okay.

11:03.320 --> 11:05.150
There's plenty of fish in the sea.

11:05.150 --> 11:06.120
If it doesn't work out,

11:06.120 --> 11:08.430
I can transfer a few people from Kuanli

11:08.460 --> 11:09.260
for you to use.

11:09.260 --> 11:10.050
Hurry up.

11:10.080 --> 11:11.500
Taking so long in the bathroom.

11:11.500 --> 11:13.310
The investigation team is almost here.

11:13.310 --> 11:15.430
[Executive Corridor]

11:13.550 --> 11:14.200
Coming, coming.

11:14.200 --> 11:14.730
Hurry up.

11:15.630 --> 11:17.380
Y-You're not going to...

11:17.460 --> 11:17.910
[Recycling from Executive Corridor]

11:17.940 --> 11:18.780
[This file is empty]

11:19.390 --> 11:21.150
Are you crazy?
You're throwing away your career.

11:21.150 --> 11:22.550
And deleted files can be recovered.

11:22.550 --> 11:24.350
I need to buy some time right now.

11:24.960 --> 11:26.760
The time it takes to recover them

11:27.000 --> 11:28.320
is enough to get to the bottom of this.

11:27.340 --> 11:27.500
[Purong Hotel]

11:27.580 --> 11:28.810
[Recycle Bin]

11:34.240 --> 11:35.030
M-Mr. Ji.

11:39.870 --> 11:40.870
Mr. Wang, this way please.

11:40.870 --> 11:41.600
Excuse me.

11:43.400 --> 11:45.060
Mr. Duan Jr., you're here too.

11:46.200 --> 11:48.150
Mr. Ji, please step aside.

11:50.070 --> 11:51.270
Please wait a moment.

11:51.910 --> 11:53.750
I've already had my subordinates

11:53.750 --> 11:55.750
get all the relevant footage ready.

11:55.750 --> 11:56.670
Let me find it.

11:56.710 --> 11:58.510
[Surveillance Footage]
[Executive Corridor]

12:02.510 --> 12:03.190
Where's the footage?

12:03.190 --> 12:04.960
[Executive Corridor]
[This file is empty]

12:03.440 --> 12:05.840
I just checked it this morning.
It was fine.

12:19.490 --> 12:20.380
Ji Feng.

12:21.640 --> 12:23.450
You've really got guts.

12:25.380 --> 12:27.240
I'll see you at the board meeting.

13:55.790 --> 13:56.520
Let's begin.

13:57.510 --> 13:58.510
Earlier this year,

13:58.510 --> 14:00.550
Mr. Marcos stayed at the hotel.

14:01.030 --> 14:02.360
Xu Miyu was his butler.

14:03.120 --> 14:04.750
She knows Mr. Marcos' habits

14:05.150 --> 14:06.950
better than anyone in the hotel.

14:07.380 --> 14:09.190
I did prepare the vase myself.

14:09.960 --> 14:12.120
I did run into Ms. Xu in the hallway.

14:12.200 --> 14:14.630
She was holding a vase

14:14.960 --> 14:17.410
and said she was going to Room 1822.

14:17.600 --> 14:20.400
I left right after
I delivered the vase to the room.

14:21.150 --> 14:23.900
I had no idea
there was a bug in the vase.

14:24.120 --> 14:25.670
I gave the room card to Miyu.

14:26.090 --> 14:27.840
I was supposed to go with her,

14:27.980 --> 14:29.250
but I got held up at the time

14:29.250 --> 14:31.450
by a guest checking in.

14:33.550 --> 14:34.480
I think...

14:35.170 --> 14:36.890
Miyu wouldn't do such a thing.

14:36.920 --> 14:38.280
Room 1822

14:38.560 --> 14:40.370
has always been cleaned by Dai.

14:41.230 --> 14:42.650
You can go ask her.

14:42.910 --> 14:43.510
Dai?

14:44.700 --> 14:47.710
[Honoring True Hospitality]

14:44.870 --> 14:47.790
After I finished
cleaning the other rooms that day,

14:48.220 --> 14:50.150
I hadn't gotten to Room 1822 yet
when I was called in

14:50.150 --> 14:51.750
to have my phone checked.

14:52.840 --> 14:54.700
My other colleagues can prove it.

14:56.670 --> 14:57.870
Anything else to add?

14:59.510 --> 15:04.000
[Honoring True Hospitality]

15:07.240 --> 15:08.360
Excuse me,

15:09.320 --> 15:10.990
when can I leave?

15:11.790 --> 15:14.030
The hotel has no right
to restrict your freedom.

15:14.030 --> 15:16.000
But until this matter
is fully investigated,

15:16.000 --> 15:18.160
you'll be suspended from your duties
and under observation.

15:18.160 --> 15:19.820
And after it's investigated?

15:20.030 --> 15:21.600
Once your actions are confirmed,

15:21.600 --> 15:24.000
you could face criminal liability.

16:18.240 --> 16:19.300
Are you okay?

16:21.020 --> 16:21.730
I'm sorry.

16:22.870 --> 16:23.630
I'm fine.

16:31.120 --> 16:32.570
I heard from my father

16:33.000 --> 16:34.730
that you're in a bad situation.

16:35.060 --> 16:35.860
Is that true?

16:37.780 --> 16:39.150
It's not that bad.

16:45.020 --> 16:45.690
Miyu,

16:47.440 --> 16:48.390
come with me.

16:51.270 --> 16:53.930
I don't want you
to face all this danger anymore.

16:54.660 --> 16:55.560
Leave Purong

16:55.650 --> 16:57.250
and come to Hong Kong with me.

17:02.030 --> 17:03.270
Mr. Tan, didn't you decide

17:03.270 --> 17:05.270
to develop your career in Shanghai?

17:10.450 --> 17:12.420
Am I not being clear enough?

17:13.510 --> 17:15.170
Do you really not understand?

17:15.829 --> 17:17.680
It actually doesn't matter where I work.

17:17.680 --> 17:19.339
What matters is where you are.

17:20.790 --> 17:22.270
I don't want you to face

17:22.270 --> 17:25.000
all this workplace politics anymore
just to make a living.

17:25.000 --> 17:26.480
I want to protect you.

17:28.099 --> 17:29.510
Let's be together.

17:31.780 --> 17:33.580
Give me a chance, okay?

17:36.720 --> 17:37.830
From now on,

17:38.880 --> 17:40.850
I won't let anyone hurt you.

17:41.480 --> 17:42.960
I will always protect you,

17:44.150 --> 17:46.150
and I'll always protect our family.

17:46.750 --> 17:47.710
I swear.

17:52.020 --> 17:52.980
Thank you.

17:54.130 --> 17:56.610
But I'm sorry.

17:57.490 --> 17:58.550
I can't go with you.

17:59.920 --> 18:01.250
Is it because of Ji Feng?

18:02.510 --> 18:03.440
Not entirely.

18:05.370 --> 18:07.230
Then is it because I came too late?

18:10.680 --> 18:12.380
It's not a matter of timing.

18:13.830 --> 18:15.920
I used to long for the kind of

18:15.920 --> 18:17.980
relationship you're talking about.

18:19.190 --> 18:21.060
But then I realized

18:22.590 --> 18:24.400
that kind of relationship completely

18:24.400 --> 18:25.640
entrusting yourself to another person

18:25.640 --> 18:26.790
isn't right for me.

18:29.750 --> 18:30.590
Mr. Tan,

18:32.620 --> 18:34.020
you're a really good man.

18:35.000 --> 18:36.550
We just didn't meet

18:36.550 --> 18:37.550
at the right time.

18:38.710 --> 18:40.030
And the future

18:41.160 --> 18:43.000
we want now is different.

18:50.350 --> 18:51.240
Thank you.

18:53.000 --> 18:55.060
Thank you for being so honest with me.

18:56.240 --> 18:57.500
I respect your choice.

19:04.160 --> 19:04.770
By the way,

19:05.880 --> 19:07.760
did you know Ji Feng has already left

19:07.760 --> 19:08.890
Purong Hotel?

19:09.380 --> 19:10.580
When did that happen?

19:11.090 --> 19:12.090
Just tonight.

19:16.100 --> 19:17.310
My father told me.

19:18.240 --> 19:19.160
He deleted

19:19.160 --> 19:22.240
the surveillance footage
outside the guest rooms to help you.

19:22.240 --> 19:23.640
The board believed

19:23.660 --> 19:25.710
he was obstructing
the hotel's investigation of you.

19:25.710 --> 19:27.930
And they decided to fire him.

19:28.810 --> 19:31.340
Miyu, they let you go?

19:31.800 --> 19:32.910
Where are you now?

19:42.210 --> 19:44.010
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

19:45.720 --> 19:47.320
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

19:49.570 --> 19:51.400
♪ People in the city ♪

19:52.310 --> 19:55.710
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

19:52.720 --> 19:53.960
Are you okay?

19:54.990 --> 19:56.320
Are you out of your mind?

19:57.180 --> 19:59.210
♪ The palms of time ♪

19:57.470 --> 20:00.070
Why did you delete
that surveillance footage?

20:00.480 --> 20:01.650
I didn't mean to.

20:00.910 --> 20:04.210
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

20:02.610 --> 20:03.790
My finger just slipped.

20:03.790 --> 20:05.350
What about your career?

20:04.650 --> 20:07.890
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

20:05.530 --> 20:07.200
Where's your sanity, Ji Feng?

20:08.020 --> 20:10.110
You worked so hard
to get where you are today.

20:08.580 --> 20:10.820
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

20:10.130 --> 20:11.500
I couldn't just stand by and watch them

20:11.500 --> 20:13.360
destroy everything you've done.

20:15.330 --> 20:16.990
So what are you going to do now?

20:18.960 --> 20:19.650
I...

20:21.030 --> 20:22.610
I'll help you find out the truth first,

20:22.610 --> 20:25.130
and we'll figure it out as we go.

20:26.390 --> 20:27.500
How?

20:28.440 --> 20:30.170
I've been thinking these days.

20:31.420 --> 20:33.510
From the sales office

20:33.530 --> 20:34.980
to Marcos's room,

20:35.270 --> 20:36.000
no one

20:36.000 --> 20:38.030
touched that vase except me.

20:38.200 --> 20:40.550
So how did that bug get in there?

20:40.880 --> 20:42.790
Did you run into anyone

20:42.790 --> 20:44.070
before you entered the room?

20:44.070 --> 20:45.030
Yes,

20:45.030 --> 20:47.400
but just in passing.

20:47.400 --> 20:49.030
None of them had a chance

20:49.030 --> 20:50.480
to plant a bug.

20:51.570 --> 20:53.790
Well, I might have a lead.

20:54.110 --> 20:55.980
I want to look into Wei Siyuan first.

20:55.980 --> 20:56.880
Wei Siyuan?

20:57.030 --> 20:57.680
Why?

20:57.960 --> 20:59.380
Marcos told me

20:59.430 --> 21:00.160
that

21:00.180 --> 21:02.050
Niu Qiankun from Jinkun Group

21:02.080 --> 21:04.270
used to have some dealings
with Wei Siyuan.

21:04.270 --> 21:06.530
So he's definitely involved.

21:06.640 --> 21:09.340
And I don't trust
the investigation team either.

21:09.340 --> 21:11.190
I want to follow him myself,

21:11.480 --> 21:13.400
see who he's been in contact with.

21:14.720 --> 21:15.780
Wait.

21:15.880 --> 21:18.130
Ms. Xu, what are you doing here?

21:18.280 --> 21:20.710
I need to deliver something to Room 1822.

21:20.760 --> 21:21.690
Are you okay?

21:21.770 --> 21:22.450
I'm fine.

21:22.480 --> 21:23.640
I'll help you pick them up.

21:23.640 --> 21:24.810
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

21:34.610 --> 21:35.870
It just occurred to me—

21:36.000 --> 21:37.530
that day in the hallway,

21:37.560 --> 21:39.510
I ran into an attendant named Dai.

21:39.880 --> 21:41.070
She's probably the only other person

21:41.070 --> 21:43.600
who had a chance
to touch that vase besides me.

21:43.660 --> 21:44.900
But I can't figure out

21:44.920 --> 21:46.310
why she would do that.

21:47.530 --> 21:49.730
Let's split up and investigate for now.

21:51.190 --> 21:52.220
And be careful.

21:54.790 --> 21:55.460
Ji Feng,

21:56.790 --> 21:57.680
thank you

21:58.140 --> 22:00.070
for trusting me unconditionally.

22:01.520 --> 22:02.330
Don't worry.

22:02.830 --> 22:04.630
Everything's gonna be alright.

22:09.510 --> 22:10.310
It'll be fine.

22:11.440 --> 22:12.410
It'll be fine.

22:26.240 --> 22:28.390
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

22:29.320 --> 22:31.340
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

22:33.300 --> 22:35.500
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

22:36.520 --> 22:38.500
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

22:40.190 --> 22:42.630
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

22:43.100 --> 22:45.250
♪ In the virtual world ♪

22:46.600 --> 22:51.860
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

22:53.540 --> 22:55.410
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

22:55.950 --> 22:59.330
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

23:00.830 --> 23:02.420
♪ Until I met you ♪

23:03.220 --> 23:06.390
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

23:06.920 --> 23:08.950
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

23:09.320 --> 23:11.050
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

23:11.510 --> 23:12.770
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

23:13.140 --> 23:14.990
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

23:15.390 --> 23:18.390
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

23:18.610 --> 23:20.190
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

23:21.180 --> 23:22.960
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

23:23.160 --> 23:24.850
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

23:25.630 --> 23:27.830
♪ Love really hurts ♪

23:29.060 --> 23:33.720
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

24:06.130 --> 24:06.890
Qingping.

24:07.960 --> 24:08.770
Ms. Xu?

24:13.240 --> 24:15.310
Ms. Xu, why are you here?

24:16.410 --> 24:17.570
I've been suspended.

24:17.570 --> 24:19.490
So I can't really go upstairs.

24:19.930 --> 24:22.720
Qingping, I want to ask you about someone.

24:23.330 --> 24:26.260
An attendant on the executive floor
named Dai Hui.

24:26.750 --> 24:28.920
The new one, Dai. What about her?

24:30.890 --> 24:33.270
In the days leading up
to the bidding meeting,

24:33.270 --> 24:35.270
did she act strangely?

24:35.600 --> 24:37.310
Like hiding things

24:37.310 --> 24:39.840
or secretly going
through guest belongings?

24:40.550 --> 24:41.960
She's always been hardworking

24:41.960 --> 24:43.110
and honest.

24:43.130 --> 24:44.930
I haven't noticed anything off.

24:46.310 --> 24:48.600
Then who does she usually hang out with?

24:49.800 --> 24:51.590
She's pretty shy.

24:51.620 --> 24:52.750
Besides

24:52.750 --> 24:54.480
the other girls in the HSKP Department,

24:54.480 --> 24:56.680
I haven't seen her close to anyone else.

24:58.050 --> 24:58.770
Oh, right,

24:58.980 --> 25:00.340
when she first came,

25:00.370 --> 25:01.480
I heard someone say

25:01.850 --> 25:03.850
a fellow Ningxin townsman of hers,

25:03.880 --> 25:06.680
who already worked at the hotel,
introduced her.

25:07.440 --> 25:08.110
Who?

25:08.130 --> 25:09.040
I'm not sure.

25:09.510 --> 25:10.440
And even if we asked,

25:10.440 --> 25:11.750
she might not tell us.

25:14.680 --> 25:15.510
What's wrong?

25:15.930 --> 25:17.780
Is it about the bidding meeting?

25:18.230 --> 25:19.630
Do you have any new clues?

25:24.160 --> 25:25.070
Miyu,

25:25.170 --> 25:28.050
all of us on the executive floor
believe in you.

25:28.400 --> 25:30.330
If you need us for anything,

25:30.350 --> 25:31.350
just ask.

25:33.160 --> 25:34.720
Thank you, Qingping.

26:00.200 --> 26:01.600
That day at the hospital,

26:02.960 --> 26:04.560
I wanted to say

26:06.160 --> 26:07.360
thank you for coming.

26:09.410 --> 26:10.240
Actually,

26:15.880 --> 26:17.610
I'm the one who should be sorry.

26:20.550 --> 26:23.180
Let's not bring up the past.

26:24.130 --> 26:25.340
It's all in the past.

26:29.840 --> 26:32.440
I heard you've run into
some trouble recently.

26:32.680 --> 26:33.530
I'm fine.

26:34.760 --> 26:35.570
I know.

26:36.550 --> 26:37.480
I don't have the right to ask.

26:37.480 --> 26:38.510
I'm really fine.

26:43.940 --> 26:45.280
Take care of yourself.

26:46.530 --> 26:47.330
Wait a minute.

26:50.830 --> 26:52.360
Actually, I came here today

26:52.830 --> 26:54.420
to tell you something.

26:57.870 --> 26:59.670
When I got home from the hospital

27:00.440 --> 27:01.920
to pack my things,

27:02.330 --> 27:04.930
I saw Lu Zhenzhen
on the phone with your sister.

27:06.250 --> 27:07.860
You must be surprised too.

27:09.150 --> 27:11.610
Those two have nothing
to do with each other.

27:11.960 --> 27:13.490
They talked for a long time.

27:14.110 --> 27:15.510
Something just felt off.

27:20.160 --> 27:22.440
-Open the door! I know you're inside!
-Yao Zhigang's not home!

27:22.440 --> 27:24.480
-He took off!
-Open the door!

27:24.480 --> 27:25.590
Pay up, Yao Zhigang!

27:25.590 --> 27:27.910
-I really have no money.
-Go!

27:28.350 --> 27:29.960
Don't come to me anymore!

27:29.960 --> 27:30.680
I have no money!

27:30.680 --> 27:31.480
Stop it!

27:32.980 --> 27:34.310
I've called the police.

27:42.640 --> 27:43.240
Tell me.

27:44.840 --> 27:46.100
Is it because of money?

27:48.240 --> 27:49.590
What money?

27:51.970 --> 27:54.260
How much do you owe those people?

27:54.510 --> 27:56.640
That's not even my debt.

27:56.640 --> 27:58.310
It's that bastard, Yao Zhigang.

27:58.310 --> 27:59.880
He racked up a huge debt,

27:59.880 --> 28:01.310
and then disappeared.

28:01.310 --> 28:02.480
What a scumbag.

28:03.720 --> 28:05.960
Tell me, was it that night?

28:08.310 --> 28:09.830
W-What night?

28:12.720 --> 28:14.640
You came to my dorm that night,

28:14.640 --> 28:17.110
pretending to ask about the guesthouse,

28:17.880 --> 28:19.400
but you were really trying

28:19.400 --> 28:20.720
to install that bugging app on my phone,

28:20.720 --> 28:21.550
weren't you?

28:22.350 --> 28:23.240
W-What?

28:23.240 --> 28:24.460
What... What app?

28:24.920 --> 28:25.680
Install what?

28:25.680 --> 28:27.940
I have no idea what you're talking about.

28:28.590 --> 28:30.110
It's fine if you don't admit it.

28:30.110 --> 28:32.070
But I'm telling you,

28:32.070 --> 28:33.240
you didn't succeed.

28:33.260 --> 28:35.520
All that work for nothing, you know that?

28:35.720 --> 28:37.530
Don't try to bluff me here.

28:37.590 --> 28:38.640
Use your brain.

28:38.640 --> 28:39.970
If you had succeeded,

28:40.000 --> 28:42.660
would I be sitting here
in front of you right now?

28:48.190 --> 28:49.580
Did you get the money?

28:53.350 --> 28:54.440
I can tell you this—

28:54.800 --> 28:56.460
you're not getting the money.

28:56.640 --> 28:58.510
It's because they're
looking for idiots like you

28:58.510 --> 29:00.350
who work for free.

29:00.400 --> 29:02.350
Bullshit! She promised me!

29:02.350 --> 29:04.000
As long as I installed that app—

29:04.000 --> 29:04.510
Who?

29:12.960 --> 29:14.400
You can keep your mouth shut.

29:14.400 --> 29:15.920
Let the masterminds speak for you

29:15.920 --> 29:17.410
while you go to jail for them.

29:17.410 --> 29:18.440
Fair trade.

29:18.590 --> 29:19.740
Everyone wins.

29:20.900 --> 29:21.550
No.

29:23.410 --> 29:25.480
Wait, don't go.

29:25.720 --> 29:27.550
I'll tell you, okay?

30:09.000 --> 30:09.970
I'm leaving.

30:13.880 --> 30:14.800
Take care.

30:38.250 --> 30:40.020
[oume Mountain Dinner]

30:42.640 --> 30:45.590
I've seen many women like you.

30:45.880 --> 30:48.350
You think you can come after my husband

30:50.350 --> 30:52.480
just because you've got a pretty face?

30:53.510 --> 30:55.400
It's laughable.

30:55.450 --> 30:56.820
Who do you think you are?

30:56.880 --> 30:58.510
I have to deal with at least

30:58.530 --> 31:00.000
10 women like you every year

31:00.000 --> 31:01.610
for my husband.

31:01.680 --> 31:02.930
[Come to Shanghai Landmark]

31:01.830 --> 31:03.750
Lu Zhenzhen somehow found out

31:03.010 --> 31:05.490
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen]
[Unknown relationship]

31:03.750 --> 31:05.790
about Yao Zhigang's gambling debts.

31:05.790 --> 31:07.160
She came straight to me

31:07.160 --> 31:09.270
and said she had a great way for me
to make money.

31:09.270 --> 31:11.880
She wanted me to install
the transmitting software

31:11.880 --> 31:13.200
for a bug onto your phone.

31:13.200 --> 31:16.480
Once they won the bid,
she'd give me 500,000

31:16.480 --> 31:17.920
to pay off my debts.

31:18.070 --> 31:19.640
You saw it today too.

31:19.640 --> 31:21.400
Those debt collectors
are at my door every day.

31:21.400 --> 31:23.790
I can't live like this anymore.

31:23.920 --> 31:24.720
The thought of

31:24.920 --> 31:27.270
making 500,000 so easily

31:27.270 --> 31:28.750
just got the better of me.

31:28.750 --> 31:30.190
I'm sorry, Miyu.

31:30.270 --> 31:32.400
I'm begging you,
please don't call the police.

31:32.400 --> 31:34.270
Lu Zhenzhen tricked me

31:34.270 --> 31:35.530
into this.

31:35.640 --> 31:36.440
I'm fine.

31:36.920 --> 31:38.780
At least we have another clue now.

31:40.680 --> 31:41.940
It's pretty clear now.

31:42.160 --> 31:44.200
Lu Zhenzhen used your sister

31:44.220 --> 31:45.420
to set you up.

31:46.270 --> 31:47.400
And considering

31:47.590 --> 31:49.720
how Wei Siyuan's wife
cursed her out to her face,

31:49.720 --> 31:52.110
there's clearly some special relationship

31:51.010 --> 31:54.950
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen] [Wei Siyuan]

31:52.110 --> 31:54.140
between her and Wei Siyuan.

31:54.180 --> 31:55.090
But

31:55.400 --> 31:57.030
I still think

31:57.510 --> 32:00.240
someone else planted the bug.

32:02.140 --> 32:03.380
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen]
[Wei Siyuan] [Unknown relationship]

32:03.480 --> 32:04.680
You didn't see Lu Zhenzhen

32:04.680 --> 32:06.340
on the surveillance footage,

32:06.440 --> 32:08.200
and she never touched the vase.

32:08.800 --> 32:11.140
Whoever planted it is key.

32:11.400 --> 32:13.030
Either she's connected to Lu Zhenzhen

32:13.030 --> 32:14.720
or to Wei Siyuan.

32:16.350 --> 32:17.240
By the way, how's the investigation

32:17.240 --> 32:19.170
on the person you suspected going?

32:19.920 --> 32:21.480
I still can't find her connection

32:21.480 --> 32:23.830
to Lu Zhenzhen and Wei Siyuan.

32:24.100 --> 32:26.190
Let's think about it differently.

32:27.510 --> 32:29.200
This kind of risky dirty work

32:29.200 --> 32:31.330
must be done by someone controllable.

32:31.920 --> 32:33.510
If I were the mastermind,

32:34.310 --> 32:36.310
I'd pick someone with a connection,

32:36.440 --> 32:37.510
but not someone

32:37.510 --> 32:38.960
who stood out too much.

32:40.350 --> 32:41.600
When she first came,

32:41.720 --> 32:42.920
I heard someone say

32:43.220 --> 32:44.160
a fellow Ningxin townsman of hers,

32:44.160 --> 32:46.350
who already worked at the hotel,

32:46.590 --> 32:47.790
introduced her.

32:47.810 --> 32:48.550
Now that you mention it,

32:48.550 --> 32:50.080
something comes to my mind.

32:50.720 --> 32:52.470
Lu Zhenzhen is from Ningxin.

32:52.720 --> 32:54.070
So is she.

32:54.920 --> 32:56.160
Luo Qingping said earlier

32:56.160 --> 32:58.130
she was introduced by a fellow townsman.

32:58.130 --> 33:00.530
Could that fellow townsman be Lu Zhenzhen?

33:08.480 --> 33:09.640
Hello, Qingping?

33:10.280 --> 33:11.780
Can you do me a favor?

33:10.660 --> 33:15.410
[Xu Miyu] [Lu Zhenzhen]
[Wei Siyuan] [Unknown relationship]

33:19.070 --> 33:20.160
Everyone,

33:19.970 --> 33:21.080
[Purong Hotel]

33:21.130 --> 33:23.790
please write down
your schedule from last week,

33:23.840 --> 33:26.290
along with every person
you came into contact with

33:26.290 --> 33:27.770
and all the details.

33:29.450 --> 33:31.540
No whispering while writing.

33:42.400 --> 33:43.240
Dai.

33:45.510 --> 33:46.400
What's wrong?

33:47.100 --> 33:48.480
You look terrible.

33:48.510 --> 33:49.320
I'm fine.

33:49.920 --> 33:51.300
Are you sick?

33:51.920 --> 33:53.350
No, I'm fine.

33:54.400 --> 33:55.680
You need to be completely honest.

33:55.680 --> 33:57.590
Write down every detail clearly.

33:57.830 --> 33:59.030
Do not hide anything,

33:59.350 --> 34:02.480
or there will be severe consequences.

34:04.570 --> 34:08.380
[Purong Hotel]

34:24.870 --> 34:31.190
[Monday]

34:38.650 --> 34:42.860
[Monday, I got up...]

34:50.300 --> 34:54.139
[Monday, I got up at 6 a.m.]

34:58.550 --> 35:00.230
[Monday, I got up at 6 a.m.]

35:04.020 --> 35:05.590
[Monday, I got up at 6 a.m.]

35:15.000 --> 35:16.040
Dai, what's wrong?

35:16.040 --> 35:17.030
You can talk to me.

35:17.030 --> 35:18.430
Don't keep it bottled up.

35:21.320 --> 35:22.660
I didn't mean to.

35:22.710 --> 35:24.680
I really didn't mean to.

35:30.100 --> 35:36.720
[General Manager's Office]

35:31.060 --> 35:31.710
Ms. Lu.

35:31.710 --> 35:32.510
You can't go in.

35:32.510 --> 35:33.360
If you don't have an appointment,

35:33.360 --> 35:34.510
you can't just go in.

35:34.510 --> 35:35.320
Ms. Lu.

35:35.320 --> 35:36.030
Ms. Lu.

35:39.610 --> 35:41.510
Why are you barging into my office?

35:41.510 --> 35:42.510
Are you out of your mind?

35:42.510 --> 35:43.590
This is a critical time right now.

35:43.590 --> 35:45.090
Aren't you giving them
something against us?

35:45.090 --> 35:46.240
I had no choice.

35:46.270 --> 35:47.330
I wanted to see you,

35:47.440 --> 35:48.990
but you sent your wife

35:49.010 --> 35:51.480
and threatened
to kick me out of Purong Hotel.

35:51.480 --> 35:53.140
I have to come beg you, Mr. Wei.

35:53.150 --> 35:55.030
Please, let me keep my job.

35:55.110 --> 35:56.470
My wife went to see you?

35:56.560 --> 35:57.780
I had no idea.

35:59.760 --> 36:02.490
Someone in the company
must have gossiped to her.

36:02.630 --> 36:03.510
Don't be mad.

36:03.960 --> 36:05.570
Once things settle down
here in a couple of days,

36:05.570 --> 36:07.420
I'll definitely find you another job.

36:07.420 --> 36:08.410
Bbetter than Purong.

36:08.410 --> 36:09.250
Okay?

36:10.300 --> 36:12.030
Don't treat me like a naive girl.

36:12.030 --> 36:13.760
I can quit.

36:14.280 --> 36:15.800
But first, give me the money you promised.

36:15.800 --> 36:17.190
Didn't I tell you?

36:17.210 --> 36:18.590
Until this bidding thing gets settled,

36:18.590 --> 36:19.960
they're not paying me.

36:20.040 --> 36:21.110
You're pushing me so hard now.

36:21.110 --> 36:22.240
How can I give you anything?

36:22.240 --> 36:23.490
If you don't give me money,

36:23.490 --> 36:24.930
how am I supposed to raise the child

36:24.930 --> 36:26.490
and pay the mortgage?

36:26.650 --> 36:27.800
Wei Siyuan, let me tell you,

36:27.800 --> 36:28.360
I can do anything

36:28.360 --> 36:29.110
for this child.

36:29.110 --> 36:30.190
Don't push me.

36:33.510 --> 36:34.240
Zhenzhen,

36:34.630 --> 36:36.110
that's my child too.

36:37.400 --> 36:39.070
You're the mother of my child.

36:39.400 --> 36:41.530
How could I not take care of both of you?

36:42.210 --> 36:43.590
Don't be so glib with me!

36:43.660 --> 36:44.790
Alright. Come here.

36:45.710 --> 36:47.390
Let's solve the problem.

36:47.410 --> 36:48.850
No need to be angry.

36:49.550 --> 36:50.360
Tell me.

37:02.740 --> 37:04.860
Lu Zhenzhen. Stop!

37:07.230 --> 37:08.230
Didn't I tell you?

37:08.230 --> 37:09.440
Just wait.

37:09.440 --> 37:10.760
Why did you come here?

37:10.760 --> 37:11.730
Wait?

37:12.070 --> 37:13.590
If we wait any longer,
my husband will be dead,

37:13.590 --> 37:15.110
and our house will be torn down!

37:15.110 --> 37:16.480
We had a deal.

37:16.480 --> 37:17.550
As soon as the bidding meeting was over,

37:17.550 --> 37:18.840
you'd give me the money immediately.

37:18.840 --> 37:19.920
It's been days now.

37:19.920 --> 37:20.970
Where's the money?

37:20.970 --> 37:22.700
I'm warning you, Lu Zhenzhen.

37:22.730 --> 37:23.880
If you don't give me the money now,

37:23.880 --> 37:25.030
next time the debt collectors come,

37:25.030 --> 37:26.890
I'll bring them right here to you.

37:27.820 --> 37:29.300
There's nothing I can do.

37:29.360 --> 37:31.190
They still haven't paid me yet.

37:31.190 --> 37:32.440
I'm anxious too.

37:32.550 --> 37:34.710
Miyao, can you just give me two more days?

37:34.710 --> 37:35.630
As soon as I get the money,

37:35.630 --> 37:36.510
I'll transfer it to you immediately.

37:36.510 --> 37:38.010
Not a cent less.

37:39.070 --> 37:41.070
Do you think I'll still believe you?

37:41.190 --> 37:42.920
You've said that so many times.

37:43.190 --> 37:44.070
Here's the deal.

37:44.070 --> 37:45.800
Write it down in black and white today,

37:45.800 --> 37:48.000
so you won't back out later. Let's go.

37:48.510 --> 37:49.360
Hey,

37:49.360 --> 37:50.000
what are you doing?

37:50.000 --> 37:50.670
Let's go!

38:01.430 --> 38:03.640
Did you install the bugging app,

38:03.670 --> 38:04.980
or did your sister?

38:05.030 --> 38:05.880
I don't know.

38:06.280 --> 38:07.630
Anyway, it wasn't me.

38:07.650 --> 38:09.300
Stop framing me, okay?

38:10.070 --> 38:11.230
What do you mean?

38:11.440 --> 38:12.670
Didn't you come to me

38:12.670 --> 38:14.320
and ask me to get Miyu's phone

38:14.320 --> 38:15.510
and install that bugging app

38:15.510 --> 38:17.070
in exchange for 500,000?

38:17.070 --> 38:18.360
You're trying to deny it now?

38:18.360 --> 38:19.070
Ma'am,

38:19.280 --> 38:20.880
you've got the wrong person.

38:21.000 --> 38:22.360
I don't even know you, okay?

38:22.360 --> 38:23.670
Do you think I'm three years old?

38:23.670 --> 38:25.030
I've got the wrong person?

38:25.030 --> 38:26.320
If you hadn't come to me,

38:26.320 --> 38:27.880
would I have ever come up with
such a despicable scheme

38:27.880 --> 38:29.070
to harm my own sister?

38:29.070 --> 38:30.670
-I'm asking you, are you even human?
-Miyao.

38:30.670 --> 38:31.200
Sit down.

38:31.230 --> 38:32.880
Don't act like a shrew here, okay?

38:32.880 --> 38:35.280
-Who are you calling a shrew?
-Lu Zhenzhen.

38:36.190 --> 38:37.190
If you don't want others to know,

38:37.190 --> 38:38.720
you shouldn't have done it.

38:38.920 --> 38:41.190
Don't think that just because you deny it,

38:41.190 --> 38:43.800
the bad things you've done
will just disappear.

38:43.800 --> 38:46.320
I don't have time
to deal with you two right now.

38:46.320 --> 38:48.120
I need to go home and feed my baby.

38:48.320 --> 38:49.030
-You can't leave.
-I'm leaving.

38:49.030 --> 38:49.880
-You can't leave!
-I need to go feed my baby.

38:49.880 --> 38:50.840
Wait a minute.

38:52.630 --> 38:53.190
Great.

38:53.590 --> 38:55.920
You brought your boyfriend here too, huh?

38:56.110 --> 38:58.190
Are the three of you trying to set me up?

38:58.190 --> 38:58.880
Ms. Lu,

39:00.370 --> 39:01.770
take a look at this first.

39:06.710 --> 39:07.280
[I'm Dai Hui, an attendant
on the executive floor of Purong Hotel.]

39:07.300 --> 39:07.810
[Not long ago, Lu Zhenzhen,
the fellow townsman who helped me]

39:07.830 --> 39:08.460
[get this job, asked me
to plant a bug in a guest's room.]

39:09.980 --> 39:11.380
I don't know this person.

39:11.750 --> 39:12.880
I don't know what she's talking about.

39:12.880 --> 39:13.940
You don't know her?

39:14.360 --> 39:15.320
Are you sure you're not the one

39:15.320 --> 39:17.320
who introduced her to Purong Hotel?

39:17.510 --> 39:18.190
No.

39:19.630 --> 39:20.630
I don't know who this person is.

39:20.630 --> 39:22.760
And I don't know what she wrote either.

39:23.510 --> 39:24.710
Then what about this?

39:24.980 --> 39:27.030
[How to Use the Bug] [Start Recording]

39:25.320 --> 39:26.730
This is the guide you gave Dai Hui

39:26.730 --> 39:28.590
to teach her how to turn on the bug.

39:29.120 --> 39:29.930
Remember?

39:30.250 --> 39:32.430
You're not the general manager
of Purong Hotel anymore.

39:32.430 --> 39:34.000
Don't wave a piece of paper at me

39:34.000 --> 39:35.000
that could be printed

39:35.000 --> 39:38.350
-at any copy shop here...
-Other than Dai Hui's fingerprints,

39:38.350 --> 39:40.320
the rest of the prints on this
should be yours.

39:40.320 --> 39:41.820
If I give this to the police,

39:41.820 --> 39:43.420
they'll give us the truth.

39:43.710 --> 39:44.510
Lu Zhenzhen,

39:45.030 --> 39:46.170
no one in this world

39:46.710 --> 39:48.510
can live in a vacuum.

39:49.630 --> 39:52.450
Everything you do leaves a trace.

39:53.000 --> 39:55.730
Do you need me
to call Dai Hui over to confront you?

40:00.560 --> 40:01.410
No need.

40:05.190 --> 40:06.030
I admit it.

40:07.070 --> 40:08.370
I asked Dai Hui

40:08.390 --> 40:10.230
to put the bug in the vase.

40:10.920 --> 40:11.710
I

40:12.230 --> 40:13.320
asked your sister

40:14.110 --> 40:16.920
to install the bugging app on your phone.

40:18.280 --> 40:19.630
Are you happy now?

40:21.920 --> 40:23.080
Why did you do that?

40:23.320 --> 40:24.520
Because I need money.

40:25.230 --> 40:26.950
How much did Wei Siyuan promise you?

40:26.950 --> 40:27.810
Eight million.

40:27.820 --> 40:30.480
And you were only
going to give me half a million?

40:30.590 --> 40:31.670
How ruthless.

40:33.110 --> 40:35.240
I need to buy an apartment in Shanghai.

40:36.070 --> 40:37.670
This is the exact amount I need.

40:37.670 --> 40:39.400
I need to give my child a future.

40:39.630 --> 40:40.630
You need money?

40:40.630 --> 40:41.510
Who doesn't?

40:41.510 --> 40:42.630
Don't I need money?

40:42.630 --> 40:44.840
Needing money is no excuse
for doing what you did.

40:44.840 --> 40:47.440
I know nothing I say now
will make a difference,

40:49.280 --> 40:50.810
but that's the whole truth.

40:50.880 --> 40:52.210
What about that guy Nie?

40:55.840 --> 40:56.800
We got divorced.

41:00.070 --> 41:01.270
What about the child?

41:04.730 --> 41:06.190
The child is Wei Siyuan's.

41:19.120 --> 41:20.610
[Meeting Room]

41:21.530 --> 41:22.520
[Mr. Wei]
